Password generator allow to generate site-specific passwords from one master password and per-site keys.

The project consists of:
- Shell script to generate passwords from the command line
- OS X Dashboard widget

Pre-requisites:
- Bash (for shell script)
- OpenSSL
- OS X for Dashboard ;)

INSTALLATION

To install Dashboard widget, navigate to this directory in OSX Finder, and open the 'Password Generator' widget. This will install the widget on your Dashboard.

